content.rendered:
Directed by Maruthi Dasari

Written by Ravi Varma Namburi. Charu Gupta

Cast Sai Dharam Tej (Sai Tej). Raashi Khanna (Aarna). Sathyaraj (Raghu Ramayya). Rao Ramesh (Anand Rao). Vijayakumar (Surya Narayana (as Vijay Kumar)). V.K. Naresh (Naresh Prasad). Murali Sharma (Damodar (as Murli Sharma)). Ajay (Nagaraju). Satyam Rajesh (Nagaraju’s brother). Gayatri Bhargavi (Raghu Ramayya’s daughter). Hari Teja (Geetha). Praveen (Harish). Bharath Reddy (Dr. Bharath). Prabha (Janaki) . Mahesh Achanta (Mahesh). Bhadram (Geetha’s brother). Srikanth Iyengar (Sai’s uncle). Venkat Prasa (Venkat). Rajitha. Rajyalakshmi. Subhash. Suhas (Suhas)

Languages Telugu

Producers Allu Aravind. K. Babu. Guru Bobba. SKN. Bunny Vasu

Production GA2 Picture. Goldmines Telefilm. UV Creation
